task.summary: - Cleaned up Tile_Description parsing. Tile_Description parameter set needs to end with '~' instead of a '.' for parsing purposes. This fixes the bug where the final period was dropped because of the 'string'.split() function. - Improved the map interface so that it's monospaced (the big characters threw the monospacing out of whack.) - Added tile discovery to the map, where known exits appear as '?' - Added features to set a room's map symbol. Defaults are set in the tiles module under each child class.
